## Configuration

Configure the VCS module under `ai.integrations.vcs` in your `app-config.yaml`:

```yaml
ai:
  integrations:
    vcs:
      provider: github
      github:
        host: github.com
```

Supported providers: `github`, `gitlab`, `bitbucket`, `azuredevops`. Only `github` is implemented in the first pass.

